meansOfImplementation - Variable in class Order
meansOfImplementation is variable which describes how order will arrive to customer (self-pickup, courier company).
mediumLengthOfString - Static variable in class Length
mediumLengthOfString variable concerns meansOfImplementation from Order class.
moneyPattern1 - Static variable in class Regex
moneyPattern1 allows to add writing with max 7 digits (min 1 digit), dot and exactly 2 digits directly after dot.
moneyPattern2 - Static variable in class Regex
moneyPattern2 allows to add writing with max 8 digits (min 1 digit), dot and exactly 1 digit directly after dot.
moneyPattern3 - Static variable in class Regex
moneyPattern3 allows to add writing with max 9 digits (min 1 digit).
moneyPrecision - Static variable in class Length
moneyPrecision variable concerns originalPrice from Item class, extraCost from Order class and averageItemPrice from Quantity class.
moneyScale - Static variable in class Length
moneyScale variable concerns originalPrice from Item class, extraCost from Order class and averageItemPrice from Quantity class.It is also used to set object of DecimalFormat (every variables concerning money are displaying on the list according to this format).
